org.gbif.doi.metadata.datacite

Class DataCiteMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.doi.metadata.datacite.DataCiteMetadata

  • public class DataCiteMetadata
extends Object
    DataCite requires at least the following metadata properties:
    • Identifier
    • Creator
    • Title
    • Publisher
    • PublicationYear
